1. *Zaustavimo* vozilo na semaforu. (Let's stop the vehicle at the traffic light.)
2. Molim vas, da *zaustavite* se na trenutak i saslušate ovo. (Please, pause for a moment and listen to this.)
3. *Zaustavimo* se ovde da se odmorimo. (Let's stop here to rest.)
4. Ako ne *zaustavimo* ovaj trend, imaćemo velikih problema. (If we don't stop this trend, we'll have big problems.)
5. Nadam se da će nas *zaustaviti* policija ako prekoračimo brzinu. (I hope the police will stop us if we exceed the speed limit.)
6. Da bismo *zaustavili* dalje širenje virusa, moramo se pridržavati mera. (To stop the further spread of the virus, we must adhere to measures.)
7. Železnica planira da *zaustavi* ovaj voz u manjem mestu. (The railway company plans to stop this train in a smaller town.)
8. Postoji mogućnost da *zaustave* proizvodnju u fabrici. (There is a possibility that they will stop production at the factory.)
9. Učinimo sve što je u našoj moći da *zaustavimo* širenje lažnih vesti. (Let's do everything in our power to stop the spread of fake news.)
10. Ukoliko ne *zaustavimo* krčenje šuma, uništićemo prirodu. (If we don't stop deforestation, we'll destroy nature.)

(Note: the word "zaustavimo" is conjugated to match the context of the sentence.)